question: Count active Patient, display their names, and programs enrolled in a table
sql:
SELECT p.patient_id, p.name, po.program_name
FROM patient p
JOIN patient_program pp ON p.patient_id = pp.patient_id
JOIN program po ON pp.program_id = po.program_id
WHERE p.voided_by IS NULL;
